rows.label: qst201401_0010
rows.name:
Huh?
Are you seriously suggesting we stop here today?

rows.label: qst201401_0020
rows.name:
Yeah...
Is there a problem?

rows.label: qst201401_0030
rows.name: Um, hello?!

rows.label: qst201401_0040
rows.name: This kind of boring, lame-o location totally saps my Girl Power!

rows.label: qst201401_0050
rows.name:
What is 'Girl Power'?
And what it got to do with location of inn?

rows.label: qst201401_0060
rows.name:
Girl Power is a girl's driving force!
Girl Power is what grants me my awesomeness in battle.

rows.label: qst201401_0070
rows.name: If Girl Power gets too low...

rows.label: qst201401_0080
rows.name: ...well, life is no longer worth living.

rows.label: qst201401_0090
rows.name: Huh? It that important?

rows.label: qst201401_0100
rows.name:
But, these inns are pretty much the same, Zakuro.
It's the same old thing, wherever you go.

rows.label: qst201401_0110
rows.name: You do sometimes exaggerate things...

rows.label: qst201401_0120
rows.name: I NEVER exaggerate!

rows.label: qst201401_0130
rows.name:
It's hard to even take proper care of your skin
in a place like this.

rows.label: qst201401_0140
rows.name: Hikari, you know this!

rows.label: qst201401_0150
rows.name:
I've noticed you've been shrinking into the background lately.
Like a little wallflower...

rows.label: qst201401_0160
rows.name: ...Wallflower...?!

rows.label: qst201401_0170
rows.name: You mean...no one notices me?

rows.label: qst201401_0180
rows.name: Ah, that came out wrong.

rows.label: qst201401_0190
rows.name:
All I mean is, you could use a little
boost in the Girl Power department.

rows.label: qst201401_0200
rows.name:
Rex, you're a guy. Don't tell me you haven't noticed
that Hikari is lacking a little something.

rows.label: qst201401_0210
rows.name:
What?!
Answer carefully, Rex.

rows.label: qst201401_0220
rows.name: Huh?

rows.label: qst201401_0230
rows.name:
Erm... I mean...
Ah... How can I...

rows.label: qst201401_0240
rows.name:
Uh... Rex looks like he's gonna blub.
Wouldn't want to be you!

rows.label: qst201401_0250
rows.name: Nia... Maybe we should step in to prevent an escalation.

rows.label: qst201401_0260
rows.name:
Huh?
I-I'll pass...

rows.label: qst201401_0270
rows.name: Getting in between those two right now'd be suicide.

rows.label: qst201401_0280
rows.name: Let Shellhead handle it.

rows.label: qst201401_0290
rows.name: Uh... Nah.

rows.label: qst201401_0300
rows.name:
Putting the Zekenator in the mix would only
exacerbate the situation, eh.

rows.label: qst201401_0310
rows.name: NOW you get some self-awareness.

rows.label: qst201401_0320
rows.name: Then we'll just observe...

rows.label: qst201401_0330
rows.name:
It's just a bit of banter.
How bad can it get?

rows.label: qst201401_0340
rows.name:
C'mon, Hikari... Isn't it time
you got a new outfit?

rows.label: qst201401_0350
rows.name:
Admit it.
When was that moth-eaten thing last in fashion?

rows.label: qst201401_0360
rows.name: 500 years ago, that's when!

rows.label: qst201401_0370
rows.name: M-Moth-eaten...?

rows.label: qst201401_0380
rows.name:
Well, at least I've got some clothes on! What you're wearing
wouldn't cover the head of a goose!

rows.label: qst201401_0390
rows.name:
Huh?
That's rich, coming from you!

rows.label: qst201401_0400
rows.name:
That look in your face...
You know I'm right!

rows.label: qst201401_0410
rows.name:
You wanna see who's got Girl Power?
It's on! Bring it!

rows.label: qst201401_0420
rows.name: Yeah? You bring it!

rows.label: qst201401_0430
rows.name:
Let's say the loser has to...ummm
...do a little dance for everyone.

rows.label: qst201401_0440
rows.name:
Well?
Think you can you handle it?

rows.label: qst201401_0450
rows.name: Oh I can handle it!

rows.label: qst201401_0460
rows.name:
But Zakuro... This is practically a done deal.
You really wanna go there?

rows.label: qst201401_0470
rows.name: You bet.

rows.label: qst201401_0480
rows.name:
It's totally a done deal. I'm looking
forward to kicking your butt.

rows.label: qst201401_0490
rows.name:
Hey, guys... Do you really think this is a good idea?
You're getting a bit aggressive...

rows.label: qst201401_0500
rows.name: Shut up, Rex!

rows.label: qst201401_0510
rows.name: ...Got it.

rows.label: qst201401_0520
rows.name: OK. Let's do this. See you at 18:00.

rows.label: qst201401_0530
rows.name:
You'd better go and work on your Girl
Power, Zakuro. Don't underestimate me.

rows.label: qst201401_0540
rows.name: I'll show you!

rows.label: qst201401_0550
rows.name:
I know the score.
See you there!
